channel.title: Interface Editor [SAVE]
channel.description:
Hi. I am in need of some help. I have edited an interface using Lin's Interface Editor. I have a question. Where do I save the interface to? I exported it to my client's cache. It didn't work. any help please? Thank you!
Skype: modcodygodex

item.title: Interface Editor [SAVE]
item.dc:creator: @sk8rdude461 sk8rdude461
item.description:
@sk8rdude461 wrote:

[quote=“BizarrePvP, post:9, topic:523909”]Ok so I am uing an Allstar base with Stupit’s Blank Client. I have an Interface Maker, RuneScape Interface Editor, and Tom’s Cache Suite. Not sure how I can get this working. Tried for about 2 hours today. Can someone please add me on Skype and help me? Thank you.
Skype: modcodygodex[/quote]
Use the interface editor if you want to modify interfaces that are already inside the cache.
Edit the interfaces how you like, and then from there export the dat.
and do what I said above.
